---
title: Sweet Potato and Parsnip Gratin with Cavolo Nero
description: Made with two sweet root vegetables which are counterbalanced with the pleasantly tangy, bitter taste of cavolo nero, our sweet potato and parsnip gratin is packed full with wholesome, comforting flavours. Stirred in a rich, creamy sauce with creme fraiche and garlic, along with mustard for a hint of a taste of vinegar, and baked until golden, this gratin is a weeknight winner.
